text: Nyanga is a province in Gabon. The provincial capital is Tchibanga. == Departments == There are six departments: * Basse-Banio Department (Mayumba) * Douigni Department (Moabi) * Doutsila Department (Mabanda) * Haute-Banio Department (Ndindi) * Mongo Department (Moulengui-Binza) * Mougoutsi Department (Tchibanga) == References == Category:Provinces of Gabon
title: Nyanga Province
